content:
A healthcare worker in #Alaska had an anaphylactic reaction & was hospitalized in ICU after receiving the #Pfizervaccine.
The woman doesn't have a history of allergies.
#Vaccine is for emergency use, still many unanswered questions.
#PfizerBioNTech
date: 'Lightning's going to strike somewhere': Juneau health care worker hospitalized, another treated...A Juneau health care worker had a "serious allergic reaction" Tuesday and was hospitalized after being injected with the COVID-19 vaccine produced by drug companies Pfizer and BioNTech, the New York...alaskapublic.org
